title: William Morris Granville Earrings
description:
These earrings are inspired by Granville, a pattern created by John Henry Dearle, who was trained by master craftsman William Morris. Dearle designed many of the later wallpapers and textiles released by Morris & Company. Ships nicely boxed and ready for gifting.

  • Dimensions: 1.75 in.
  • Materials: solid brass, giclee print, hand gilded faux silver, ear wires are hypo-allergenic
